race.comment: TIGGERLONG SNOW (6) is a progressive dog who scored his 4th career win last time at Nowra, scoring by 4 lengths (29.67). Won at his only start from this box. Can measure up again. LATCH ON (4) goes very well this course and distance starting 22 times for nine wins and seven minors. In the money last time at this track (30.39) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 0.8 lengths second. Looks suited here and can measure up. BLUE SWALLOW (1) comes here following a placing in handy time (25.87) over 457m at Temora. Has the ability and can measure up. SHAYNA BALE (7) should be thereabouts after filling a top-three spot most recently.
